\c 18
\s Umfanekiso womfelokazi ophikelelayo
\p
\v 1 Wasebatshela lomfanekiso esenzela ukuthi bafanele ukukhuleka isikhathi sonke\x + 11.5-7. 21.36. Roma 12.12. Efe. 6.18. Kol. 4.2. 1 Thes. 5.17.\x*, njalo bengadinwa\x + 2 Kor. 4.1,16. Gal. 6.9. Efe. 3.13. 2 Thes. 3.13.\x*,
\v 2 wathi: Kwakukhona emzini othile umahluleli othile, owayengesabi uNkulunkulu, njalo engahloniphi muntu\x + 18.4. 20.13. Mat. 21.37. Heb. 12.9.\x*;
\v 3 kwakukhona futhi kulowomuzi umfelokazi othile, njalo wayefika kuye, esithi: Ngiphindiselele esitheni sami.
\v 4 Kodwa kavumanga okwesikhathi; kodwa emva kwalezizinto wathi ngaphakathi kwakhe: Lanxa ngingamesabi uNkulunkulu, ngingahloniphi muntu\x + 18.4. 20.13. Mat. 21.37. Heb. 12.9.\x*,
\v 5 kodwa ngoba lumfelokazi engikhathaza, ngizamphindiselela\x + 11.8.\x*, hlezi angaze ekucineni angidinise\x + 1 Kor. 9.27.\x*.
\v 6 INkosi yasisithi: Zwanini umahluleli ongalunganga akutshoyo\x + 16.8, 9.\x*.
\v 7 Kanti uNkulunkulu\x + Isam. 6.10.\x* kayikwenza impindiselo\x + 21.22.\x* yabakhethiweyo bakhe abakhalayo kuye emini lebusuku\x + Mat. 24.22,24,31. Roma 8.33. Kol. 3.12. 2 Tim. 2.10. Tit. 1.1. 1 Pet. 1.2. 2.9. Isam. 17.14.\x*, lanxa ebekezela ngabo\x + Jak. 5.7. 2 Pet. 3.9.\x*?
\v 8 Ngiyalitshela ukuthi uzahle enze\x + 2 Pet. 3.8,9. Heb. 10.37.\x* impindiselo yabo\x + 21.22.\x*. Kodwa-ke nxa iNdodana yomuntu ifika, izathola ukholo yini emhlabeni?
\s UmFarisi lomthelisi ethempelini
\p
\v 9 Wasekhuluma lumfanekiso lakwabathile\x + 10.29. 16.15.\x* ababezithemba\x + 2 Kor. 1.9.\x* ukuthi balungile, futhi bedelela abanye, \add wathi\add*:
\v 10 Abantu ababili benyukela ethempelini ukuyakhuleka; omunye engumFarisi\x + 2 Kho. 20.5,8. Seb. 3.1. Luka 18.14. 1 Kho. 10.5.\x*, lomunye engumthelisi\x + Mat. 18.17.\x*.
\v 11 UmFarisi wema wazikhulekela kanje \add wathi\add*: Nkulunkulu, ngiyakubonga ukuthi kanginjengabanye abantu\x + 18.13. Hlab. 135.2. Mark. 11.25.\x*, abaphangi, abangalunganga, izifebe, loba lanjengalumthelisi\x + 1 Kor. 5.10,11. 6.10.\x*.
\v 12 Ngizila ukudla kabili ngeviki\x + Mat. 9.14. 5.33.\x*, nginikela okwetshumi\x + 11.42. Nani 18.21.\x* kwakho konke engikuzuzayo\x + 21.19.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa umthelisi emi khatshana\x + 18.13. Hlab. 135.2. Mark. 11.25.\x* wayengathandi lokuphakamisela amehlo ezulwini\x + Ezra 9.6. Luka 6.20.\x*, kodwa watshaya isifuba sakhe, esithi: Nkulunkulu, ngihawukele mina soni\x + 23.48.\x*.
\v 14 Ngithi kini: Lo wehlela endlini yakhe\x + 18.10.\x* elungisisiwe kulalowayana\x + Seb. 13.39. Roma 2.13. 3.24.\x*; ngoba wonke oziphakamisayo uzathotshiswa, kodwa ozithobayo uzaphakanyiswa\x + Mat. 23.12.\x*.
\s Ukubusiswa kwabantwana abancane
\p
\v 15 Basebeletha kuye lensane, ukuze azibambe; kodwa abafundi be\add ku\add*bona babakhuza.
\v 16 Kodwa uJesu wazibizela kuye wathi: Vumelani abantwana abancane beze kimi, lingabenqabeli, ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu ungowabanje\x + Mat. 19.13-15 Mark. 10.13-16.\x*.
\v 17 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Loba ngubani ongemukeli umbuso kaNkulunkulu njengomntwana omncane, kasoze angene kuwo\x + Mark. 10.15.\x*.
\s Ijaha elinothileyo
\p
\v 18 Umbusi\x + Joha. 3.1.\x* othile\x + Mat. 19.16-29. Mark. 10.17-30.\x* wasembuza, esithi: Mfundisi olungileyo, ngenzeni ukuze ngidle ilifa lempilo elaphakade?
\v 19 Kodwa uJesu wathi kuye: Ungibizelani \add ngokuthi\add* olungileyo? Kakho olungileyo, ngaphandle koyedwa, uNkulunkulu\x + 10.25-28.\x*.
\v 20 Uyayazi imilayo \add ethi\add*: Ungafebi, ungabulali, ungebi, ungafakazi amanga, hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko\x + Eks. 20.12-16.\x*.
\v 21 Yena wasesithi: Konke lokhu ngikugcinile kusukela ebutsheni bami.
\v 22 Kodwa uJesu esizwa lezizinto wathi kuye: Usaswele ulutho olulodwa; thengisa konke olakho, wabele abayanga, njalo uzakuba lempahla eligugu ezulwini; njalo uze lapha ungilandele.
\v 23 Kodwa yena esizwa lezizinto wadana kakhulu; ngoba wayenothile kakhulu.
\p
\v 24 Kwathi uJesu ebona ukuthi usedane kakhulu wathi: Abalenotho bazangena ngokulukhuni kangakanani embusweni kaNkulunkulu.
\v 25 Ngoba kulula ukuthi ikamela lingene ngentunja yenalithi, kulokuthi umuntu onothileyo angene embusweni kaNkulunkulu.
\v 26 Aba\add ku\add*zwayo basebesithi: Pho kungasindiswa bani?
\v 27 Kodwa yena wathi: Izinto ezingenzekiyo ebantwini ziyenzeka kuNkulunkulu\x + Tit. 1.5.\x*.
\s Umvuzo wokuzidela
\p
\v 28 UPetro wasesithi: Khangela, thina sitshiye konke, sakulandela.
\v 29 Wasesithi kubo: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kakho umuntu otshiye indlu, kumbe abazali, kumbe abafowabo, kumbe umka\add khe\add*, kumbe abantwana, ngenxa yombuso kaNkulunkulu,
\v 30 ongayikwemukela okuphindwe kanengi\x + Jobe 42.10.\x* kulesisikhathi, lesikhathini esizayo impilo elaphakade\x + Mark. 10.30.\x*.
\s UJesu ukhuluma ngokuhlupheka kwakhe
\p
\v 31 Wasezithathela abalitshumi lambili, wathi kubo: Khangelani, senyukela eJerusalema\x + Mat. 20.17-19. Mark. 10.32-34. Mat. 16.21.\x*, futhi konke okulotshiweyo ngabaprofethi ngeNdodana yomuntu kuzagcwaliseka\x + Hlab. 22.1. Isa. 53.1.\x*.
\v 32 Ngoba izanikelwa kwabezizwe, iyangiswe\x + Joha. 18.32.\x*, ithukwe\x + Seb. 14.5.\x*, ikhafulelwe ngamathe\x + Mark. 10.34.\x*,
\v 33 ba\add yi\add*tshaye ngesiswepu bayibulale; njalo ngosuku lwesithathu izabuya ivuke.
\v 34 Kodwa bona kabaqedisisanga lutho ngalezizinto\x + 2.50. Mark. 9.32. Joha. 12.16.\x*, lalinkulumo yayifihlakele kubo, njalo kabaziqedisisanga izinto ezazitshiwo\x + 9.45.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa kwesiphofu
\p
\v 35 Kwasekusithi esesondela\x + Mat. 20.29-34. Mark. 10.46-52.\x* eJeriko\x + 19.1. Mat. 20.29. Mark. 10.46.\x*, isiphofu esithile sasihlezi eceleni kwendlela\x + Mat. 20.30.\x* siphanza;
\v 36 sathi sisizwa ixuku lisedlula, sabuza ukuthi kuyini lokho\x + 15.26.\x*.
\v 37 Basebesitshela bathi: UJesu weNazaretha uyedlula.
\v 38 Sasesimemeza, sisithi: Jesu, Ndodana kaDavida, ngihawukela!
\v 39 Ababehamba phambili basebesikhuza ukuthi sithule; kodwa samemeza kakhulukazi, \add sisithi\add*: Ndodana kaDavida, ngihawukele\x + Mark. 10.48. Mat. 20.31.\x*!
\v 40 UJesu wema-ke walaya ukuthi silethwe kuye; sathi sesisondele wasibuza,
\v 41 esithi: Ufuna ukuthi ngikwenzeleni? Sasesisithi: Nkosi, ukuthi ngibuye ngibone.
\v 42 UJesu wasesithi kuso: Buya ubone! Ukholo lwakho lukusindisile\x + Mark. 10.52.\x*.
\v 43 Njalo sahle sabuya sabona, samlandela, sidumisa uNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 15.31.\x*; labantu bonke be\add ku\add*bona badumisa uNkulunkulu\x + 5.26. 9.43. 13.17. 19.37.\x*.
